Use these workflows on demand.

## Running the server
- `uv run server.py`

## Code quality
- `uv run ruff check .`, `uv run ruff format .`

## Tests
- `uv run pytest`, optionally with `-v`, `-k`, and `--cov`

## Docker
- Build: `docker build -t mcp-piwik-pro .`

See @README.md for full examples.

